    <entry>
      <title>完全背包</title>
      <link href="/2023/11/18/%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E8%83%8C%E5%8C%85/"/>
      <url>/2023/11/18/%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E8%83%8C%E5%8C%85/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Introduction"><a href="#Introduction" class="headerlink" title="Introduction"></a>Introduction</h1><p><a href="http://marxistzgwl.github.io./2023/11/18/01%E8%83%8C%E5%8C%85/">书接上文</a></p><ol><li><p>本文面向的人群：</p><ul><li><p>已经有01背包的基础</p></li><li><p>希望通过例题掌握完全背包</p></li></ul></li><li><p>本文的主要内容</p></li><li><p>本文参考</p><ul><li>背包九讲</li></ul></li></ol><h1 id="1-完全背包问题"><a href="#1-完全背包问题" class="headerlink" title="1. 完全背包问题"></a>1. 完全背包问题</h1><p>n个物品和容量为c的背包，每种物品可以无限地进行选择，物品的重量为w[i],价值为v[i]，求解哪些物品装入背包可以是的背包中的物品价值总和最大？</p><blockquote><p>w[i] 是 weight[i]的缩写， v[i] 是value[i]的缩写, c是capacity的缩写</p></blockquote><h1 id="2-思路"><a href="#2-思路" class="headerlink" title="2. 思路"></a>2. 思路</h1><p>基于01背包，我们很容易将<code>dp[i][j]</code>定义为前i件物品装容量为j的背包的答案。<br>我们尝试写出状态转移方程：<br>$$<br>d[i][j] &#x3D; max\begin{cases}<br>dp[i - 1][j] &amp; j &lt; w[i] \ \<br>dp[i][j - w[i]] + v[i] &amp; j &gt;&#x3D; w[i]<br>\end{cases}<br>$$<br>基于以上思路，我们写出代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">j</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>; j &lt;= c; j++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (j &gt;= w[i]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            dp[i][j] = max(dp[i - <span class="number">1</span>][j], dp[i][j - w[i]] + v[i]);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            dp[i][j] = dp[i - <span class="number">1</span>][j];</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们可以观察到，这样的代码和01背包的代码几乎是一模一样，我们再次给出01背包的代码用于对比。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">j</span> <span class="operator">=</span> w[i]; j &lt;= c; j++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (j &gt;= w[i]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            dp[i][j] = max(dp[i - <span class="number">1</span>][j], dp[i - <span class="number">1</span>][j - w[i]] + v[i]);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            dp[i][j] = dp[i - <span class="number">1</span>][j];</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以观察到俩者唯一的区别就在于状态转移方程的不同。</p><h1 id="3-优化"><a href="#3-优化" class="headerlink" title="3. 优化"></a>3. 优化</h1><p>很显然我们的代码可以进行空间优化。<br>如果你已经阅读过01背包的优化方式，那么这里的优化方式和01背包的是一模一样的。不在进行过多的赘述。直接给出代码：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">j</span> <span class="operator">=</span> w[i]; j &lt;= c; j++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">dp[j] = max(dp[j], dp[j - w[i]] + v[i]);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>也请你对比一下和01背包空间优化之后的代码的不同。主要的不同点在于01背包的第二层循环是<code>c ~ w[i]</code>, 而完全背包的第二层循环是<code>w[i] ~ c</code>。</p><h1 id="4-问题变形"><a href="#4-问题变形" class="headerlink" title="4. 问题变形"></a>4. 问题变形</h1><p>问题可以变形为求装满背包所使用物品的最小个数，这个时候的状态转移方程变为：</p><p><code>dp[j] = min(dp[j], dp[j - w[i]] + 1)</code></p><h1 id="5-总结"><a href="#5-总结" class="headerlink" title="5. 总结"></a>5. 总结</h1><p>完全背包模型是在01背包模型基础上进行得到的，所以代码也比较相似。请注意完全背包模型和01背包模型俩种在转台转移上的异同。</p><h1 id="6-例题训练"><a href="#6-例题训练" class="headerlink" title="6. 例题训练"></a>6. 例题训练</h1><p><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/perfect-squares/description/">279. 完全平方数 - 力扣（LeetCode）</a></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">numSquares</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> n)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span>[] dp = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">int</span>[n + <span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">        Arrays.fill(dp, <span class="number">100000</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        dp[<span class="number">0</span>] = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        dp[<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">1</span>; i * i &lt;= n; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">j</span> <span class="operator">=</span> i * i; j &lt;= n; j++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                dp[j] = Math.min(dp[j], dp[j - i * i] + <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> dp[n];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p><strong>文章推荐</strong></p><ul><li><a href="http://marxistzgwl.github.io./2023/11/18/01%E8%83%8C%E5%8C%85/">01背包</a></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
